  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\n\nUsually users set amount, then asset, then select From and To when sending transaction.\nIf in field TO scan ethereum address (i.e. `ethereum: 0xcf2272205cc0cf96Cfbb9Dd740BD681D1E86901E` - all previous parameters except From will be reset. \nIt is very common flow so issue is very visible.\n\n#### Expected behavior\n Asset and Amount are preserved, can sign transaction\n\n#### Actual behavior\n Asset and Amount are reset, need to change them second time\n<img width=\"244\" alt=\"screencast 2019-12-04 15-54-15 mp4 2019-12-04 15-55-28\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/70153032-8b92dd80-16ae-11ea-8106-22c896d324a5.png\">\n\n### Reproduction\n\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\n\n- Open Status\n- Create multiaccount > Send\n- Change Asset and Amount\n- Scan valid ethereum address\n\n### Additional Information\n- Status version: nightly 04.12.2019\n- Operating System: Android- iOS",
